snippet.textDisplay:
My Season 3 Cast - LA people within the K&J reality demographic:

1) Chris Klemons (sarcastic)
2) Morgan Adams (sarcastic)
3) Mariah Amato (dancer/humour/heart/competitor)
4) Irene Walton (heart/humour - side note; pleasing Gabbie Hanna/Megan Batoon fans).
4) Cedric Botelho (to please Trisha fans, plus energy/dancer/accent/heart).
5) Sean Van Der Wilt (as above).
6/7/8) Musicians who play instruments to help with bonding/entertainment (can only think of people outside of k&j demographic, like Julia Nunes or Tessa Violet).
9/10) Beauty/gossip people to keep that demographic happy.
11/12) A fitness guy & girl to keep competition on their toes.
13/14) Philosophical/clever folk to help with more stimulating conversation, & for the more intellectual challenges.
15/16) Past contestants - Viewers vote from season 1 & 2.

This would be a great mix of people, & a wonderful batch for group bonding/entertainment/energy/authenticity... Whilst also very much within their viewing demographic 😊❤

Other suggestions:
Pop instruments in the house next time guys (just tell contestants originals only, so you don't get copywrited)..... & Maybe create a jukebox/playlist with copyright free music for the dancers to create some entertainment/energy haha... These would help keep the contestants spirits up a little more (at least for a few hours in the evenings), which would probably make a world of difference... Plus give them something to talk about/bond further over ❤

I'd also add a "bonding box" & make contestants pick out questions/topics for group discussion... So its more than just competitions, voting & winner/loser announcing 😊❤

Good job guys - Great season... & Congrats Lena 🌹🌈☀
